RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 47. Allowance Purse 13376. FOR FILLIES THREE YEARS OLD. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 20 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since January 5 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since December 5 Allowed 4 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: INARA led throughout, prevailed. ETHIC STRIKE outside bid, gamely. OMARIS MY LOVE close up, gave way.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 29. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 20 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since January 5 Allowed 2 l bs. A Race Since December 5 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: LA BELLA GINA steady advance outside, up. EMBLEMATICA pressed pace, up for place. RECOMENDADA set pace, caught late. INNOVADORA best of rest. COLEGIACION improved position. LADY HELEN weakened. NELLS PRINCESS trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 49. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE FEBRUARY 5 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. 5# A clasf. $4,000 y debts Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BACCARAT HONOR led, drew off. IRISH THUNDER set pace, second best. MAK HERO gave way. LADY CLOVERLY weakened. STRONGER WITH YOU stalked pace, weakened. OFRENDA dropped back. BELKITA trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 1 1/8M Dirt CR: 36. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 20 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since January 5 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since De cember 5 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: NEGOCIADOR chased, led, drew off. MAXIMILIANUM second best. CUMBA'S DREAM best of rest. PREDILECTO set pace, weakened. EL TROMPETISTA weakened. CONCERTO PAU failed to menace. CHICO'S BOY trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 6F Dirt CR: 80. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 20 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since January 5 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since December 5 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FREEDONIA led throughout. LIGHT OF THE WORLD second best inside. BREVET OFFICER grudgingly. LETS PLAY HARDBALL outisde, gaining. SAVARO chased, weakened, lame. IL PIRATA stalked pace, weakened. RYBOLT improved position. DIVINING STAR improved position. DON'T MAKE IT EASY weakened. PULL A FREDDIE trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 77. Claiming Purse 6500. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON TWO RACES SINCE FEBRUARY 5 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $14,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 20 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since January 5 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since December 5 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: WHAT A BEAST rallied, drew off. LOVE IN PARADISE second best. ED'S ROCKET set pace, gave way. BEACH TRAFFIC off slowly, finished well. REDOUX improved position. MR. BUCK failed to menace. CAPTAIN dropped back. CODIGO VEINTIUNO broke in air, off slowly. YESTERYEAR dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 6F Dirt CR: 82. Stakes Purse 54260. Clasico Luis Munoz Marin (Grade III).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: COMISIONADO off pace, steady advance inside. CRIOLLITO drew clear, caught. GOLPEADOR rail, bit tight 500, gaining. PUSHI PUENTE late gain. EL SALSERO slow early, hustled along. CONDESCENDIENTE some late gain. AGUILA BLANCA chased, weakened. SURI BOY trailed.
